    #team.tab-pane.company-tab--team role="tabpanel"
      h1.team-headline
        span.founder Founders
        ' ,
        span.manager
          ' Partners
        ' &amp;
        span.partner
          ' Collaborators
      ul.team
        li.team-member.team-member--founder
          figure.team-member-image
            img alt="Zaiste" height="200" src="/assets/images/team/zaiste.jpg" width="200" /
          h3.team-member-name Zaiste
          p
            'Zaiste is a software technologist & entrepreneur. He also started two international tech conferences (RuPy & Polyconf). Before founding Nukomeet he worked the in banking industry. He studied at Adam Mickiewicz University, Paris-Sud 11 University, HEC Paris & Télécom ParisTech. He regulary blogs at zaiste.net. He speaks English, French and Polish. 
        li.team-member.team-member--founder
          figure.team-member-image
            img alt="Alban" height="200" src="/assets/images/team/alban.jpg" width="200" /
          h3.team-member-name Alban Leveau-Vallier
          p
           'Born in France, raised in Spain and Belgium, he studied at the École normale supérieure, the Sorbonne and HEC Paris, He worked at the French Embassy in Cuba, at HSBC Bank in Brazil, as a French teacher at the Saint Petersburg State University and as a social media consultant with parisian startups. In 2009 he founded Socialter, an organization promoting technology for social change. In 2011 he founded Nukomeet. He speaks French, English, Spanish, Portuguese, Italian, Russian.
        li.team-member.team-member--manager
          figure.team-member-image
            img alt="Julien" height="200" src="/assets/images/team/julien.jpg" width="200" /
          h3.team-member-name Julien Muresianu
          p
            'After studies in mathematics and statistics at École Polytechnique, ENSAE ParisTech and Sciences Po Paris, Julien worked as an economist at the French Embassy in Cuba, a lead researcher at the French Development Agency, an economy teacher at Sciences Po Paris, and as consultant for Société Générale board of directors between São Paulo, New York, Paris and Beirut. He is now focusing on data science, using clojure, java, R, and lots of maths. he speaks French, English, Spanish,Portuguese, and Japanese
        li.team-member.team-member--manager
          figure.team-member-image
            img alt="Bartłomiej" height="200" src="/assets/images/team/bartlomiej.jpg" width="200" /
          h3.team-member-name Bartłomiej Wiaduch
          p
           'Bartek is a Rails wizard who likes to build the most complex systems from casting his spells. His magic began from testing banking systems. He gained knowledge in Economics and Informatics from Poznań University of Economics, gave him analytical approach to life. He speaks English, Polish and Russian.
        li.team-member.team-member--manager
          figure.team-member-image
            img alt="" height="200" src="/assets/images/team/tomkuk.jpg" width="200" /
          h3.team-member-name Tomek Kuklis
          p
           'Tomasz is a fast and highly skilled craftsman. He uses heavily Ruby on Rails and has a taste for the latest javascript frameworks to build web and mobile applications. He attended Koszalin University of Technology and Instituto Superior Técnico, where he studied Computer Science. He speaks English and Polish.
        li.team-member.team-member--manager
          figure.team-member-image
            img alt="Adrien" height="200" src="/assets/images/team/adrien.jpg" width="200" /
          h3.team-member-name Adrien Giboire
          p
            'Adrien is a self-taught man. His motto is "a real developer can create anything independently of the technology". He has a strong curiosity, rigour and eagerness to learn new stuff with a focus on sexyness, usability and performance. He uses mainly Ruby and JavaScript, and speaks French and English.
